{"tid":2222184,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"學生資產被外人破壞 XGDX決定更嚴謹監控學生","createTime":"2020-09-29T02:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T08:25:03.000Z","uid":89767,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d66dfe85970e79aeb0c1d2a76d17cc4118169512","tid":2222184,"uid":89767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:35:01.000Z","msg":"【校園新聞】校方公布「新」保安安排 將抽樣搜查個人物品及檢查UID<br />\n<br />\n行政及財務副校長羅哲基昨日（9月28日）經電郵公布，在對最新情況進行定期審查後，校方決定重新制定進入本部大樓及百周年校園的安排，即時實施更嚴謹的保安措施。<br />\n<br />\n電郵提到獲授權的人士可能會對出入校園人士進行檢查，因此<span class=\"red\">學生和教職員由任何入口進入校園時，應攜帶有效的UID卡，而訪客則需提供相關證明文件</span>。未能提供相關證明文件的訪客有機會需提供個人資料以供校方記錄。此外，獲授權的職員可於校園入口隨機檢查進入校園入士的袋及隨身物品。上述措施亦適用於駕駛車輛進入校園的人員。<br />\n<br />\n校園電視向校方查詢有關安排，回覆稱以上目的是減少與大學事務無關的訪客進入校園，希望同學及職員諒解及合作。本台曾提問有關搜查訪客物品的準則，惟<span class=\"red\">校方只表示會抽樣搜查，沒有明確提供準則</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cXzELNo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcXzELNo.jpg&h=04f4aba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dv8x5Ns.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDv8x5Ns.jpg&h=fb2b9bbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkucampustv/photos/a.280176058717764/3339566209445385/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkucampustv%2Fphotos%2Fa.280176058717764%2F3339566209445385%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=923b7b30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkucampustv/photos/a.280176058717764/3339566209445385/?type=3</a>"},{"pid":"d96b6f109b62871d60ebd3391845cfe6c46ca189","tid":2222184,"uid":68689,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:37:40.000Z","msg":"果時有保安企係到都唔做野 唔通呢家講一講就做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd904e898a055f4725909c9fa488881f99152df","tid":2222184,"uid":89767,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:38:41.000Z","msg":"幾十人衝入校園搞破壞<br />\n成班保安企喺度乜都唔做睇住人走<br />\n平時學生搞活動就識得出嚟拉線打壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CYkXxtV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCYkXxtV.png&h=dbc10ae6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6a2fecd8ed7dc73cd118beb16e99a9e0eaec489","tid":2222184,"uid":89767,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:40:55.000Z","msg":"搭晒膊頭好friend喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/62iigWz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F62iigWz.png&h=9ae8ab6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"518a7fca4c8a01e64fee05c2f7bd3500619655c5","tid":2222184,"uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:41:36.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勾結"},{"pid":"e9902a36de27ad928bffee53ff59bbed0fe1b3d1","tid":2222184,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:45:13.000Z","msg":"XGDX 保安收晒片架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收左幾多錢呀"},{"pid":"7497bc58bb8d1669aecf569b3fee5bcee6b37433","tid":2222184,"uid":89767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:46:31.000Z","msg":"學生會旗幟豈容你班廢老破壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KLexmp8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKLexmp8.jpg&h=0a8afce7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c9e47c565c136b280bbc18b15a40a18cdddca39","tid":2222184,"uid":89767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"518a7fca4c8a01e64fee05c2f7bd3500619655c5","tid":2222184,"uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit