h=103b0148&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2310d5d751cbb52c697693a8d2cd2b153f8f8d1d","tid":2222184,"uid":998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d66dfe85970e79aeb0c1d2a76d17cc4118169512","tid":2222184,"uid":89767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:35:01.000Z","msg":"【校園新聞】校方公布「新」保安安排 將抽樣搜查個人物品及檢查UID<br />\n<br />\n行政及財務副校長羅哲基昨日（9月28日）經電郵公布，在對最新情況進行定期審查後，校方決定重新制定進入本部大樓及百周年校園的安排，即時實施更嚴謹的保安措施。<br />\n<br />\n電郵提到獲授權的人士可能會對出入校園人士進行檢查，因此<span class=\"red\">學生和教職員由任何入口進入校園時，應攜帶有效的UID卡，而訪客則需提供相關證明文件</span>。未能提供相關證明文件的訪客有機會需提供個人資料以供校方記錄。此外，獲授權的職員可於校園入口隨機檢查進入校園入士的袋及隨身物品。上述措施亦適用於駕駛車輛進入校園的人員。<br />\n<br />\n校園電視向校方查詢有關安排，回覆稱以上目的是減少與大學事務無關的訪客進入校園，希望同學及職員諒解及合作。本台曾提問有關搜查訪客物品的準則，惟<span class=\"red\">校方只表示會抽樣搜查，沒有明確提供準則</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cXzELNo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcXzELNo.jpg&h=04f4aba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dv8x5Ns.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDv8x5Ns.jpg&h=fb2b9bbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkucampustv/photos/a.280176058717764/3339566209445385/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkucampustv%2Fphotos%2Fa.280176058717764%2F3339566209445385%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=923b7b30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkucampustv/photos/a.280176058717764/3339566209445385/?type=3</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:05:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">影撚到你班垃圾企起側邊阿，炒幾個先啦起碼</span>"},{"pid":"523178833ca75968c1281012b988203cfdcbf32c","tid":2222184,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:07:06.000Z","msg":"啲報安都唔做嘢"},{"pid":"2a84c2a7bb99f8281fa41ddfd2859731e45a5e83","tid":2222184,"uid":89767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T06:13:01.000Z","msg":"重建連儂牆 辛苦港大手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4fb28feb5a6520f6fef132c27f057f420004f5","tid":2222184,"uid":89767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:59:57.000Z","msg":"【校園新聞】再有破壞連儂牆片段流出 港大保安：麻煩曬 <br />\n<br />\n連接百周年校園及本部校園大學街（U-Street）的連儂牆和祭壇早前於9月26日傍晚約7時被約30名不明人士破壞。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳其中一名破壞者的片段，片中見到有多名自稱愛國人士用手撕走連儂牆文宣，有人用垃圾袋接下文宣。期間有一名同學質問在場人士是否港大學生，有破壞者反駁「呢度係香港呀！」。<br />\n<br />\n影片亦見到在場沒有保安阻止在場人士破壞連儂牆，保安只呼籲在場人士離開，並說：「得啦得啦走啦走啦，麻煩曬麻煩曬，好無？唔該啦唔該啦。」破壞者其後從香港大學站A2出口離開，並說「我哋香港人，你垃圾，曱甴！」、「我哋愛國，香港人清理香港、清理垃圾！」。保安其後趕到電梯，並說「Thanks it's ok！」，一度豎起拇指。<br />\n<br />\n本台就此事已向港大傳訊及公共事務處查詢，截稿前未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100038531136264/videos/323782005582835/?extid=lyFG3P5iuYATfcuh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100038531136264%2Fvideos%2F323782005582835%2F%3Fextid%3DlyFG3P5iuYATfcuh&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=e7257701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100038531136264/videos/323782005582835/?extid=lyFG3P5iuYATfcuh</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/3341230445945628/?vh=e&amp;extid=8AT5O8NfZebmKtHg&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F279926822076021%2Fposts%2F3341230445945628%2F%3Fvh%3De%26extid%3D8AT5O8NfZebmKtHg%26d%3Dn&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=a8724e45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/279926822076021/posts/3341230445945628/?vh=e&amp;extid=8AT5O8NfZebmKtHg&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"a939035da96c3c4f7c702457718da4e0260853a1","tid":2222184,"uid":89767,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fd1ouPL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffd1ouPL.j