係抽查30歲以下<br />\n藍絲？唔查"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:09:45.000Z","msg":"見到大陸樣 老人 唔查"},{"pid":"3ec719819b3b42348c810f877df485c006727f9a","tid":2222184,"uid":89767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a939035da96c3c4f7c702457718da4e0260853a1","tid":2222184,"uid":89767,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fd1ouPL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffd1ouPL.jpg&h=bf4b0012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舉咩姆指<br />\n講咩麻煩晒<br />\n你班保安做緊乜嘢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:11:58.000Z","msg":"9.29 重建港大連儂牆 <br />\n<br />\n【學苑即時】9月26日晚七時許有約三十名身分不明人士闖入香港大學校園範圍內，撕毀位於大學街上層的三幅連儂牆。香港大學學生會今（9月29日）籌辦「重建港大連儂牆」行動，號召同學到大學街上層重建連儂牆，並遊行至鈕魯詩樓前向校方遞公開信。<br />\n<br />\n同學發現於鈕魯詩樓前駐守的保安中有一人面貌熟悉，懷疑其為先前網上公開片段中，以手勢和言語「歡送」撕毀連儂牆的不明人士離開的保安，該名<span class=\"red\">謝姓保安的職員編號為CSHKU 1021</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etuUBxJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetuUBxJ.jpg&h=fbe4ac79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/393883453958717/posts/4668541163159570/?extid=CvicF79I7HxcAZRd&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F393883453958717%2Fposts%2F4668541163159570%2F%3Fextid%3DCvicF79I7HxcAZRd%26d%3Dn&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=64e16236\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/393883453958717/posts/4668541163159570/?extid=CvicF79I7HxcAZRd&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"d07d5512bdc39722468dcb710d4dc558cd329683","tid":2222184,"uid":108022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:21:45.000Z","msg":"投訴班保安同保安主管<br />\n幢係到一6木咁睇住D賤人破壞"}]}